9
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:05,840
Those within the Vermilion Bird Gate are also officials.

10
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:10,000
Ren Shuaijian, Biao Fengzhe, Li,

11
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:16,120
Bo Jiejing,

12
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:21,880
Bei Juanzhe,

13
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:34,000
Ji,

14
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:40,400
Yan Junyue,

15
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,960
Ming Nalan, Yuyu.

16
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,840
Eunuch Qin

17
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,560
is reaching his hands

18
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,240
