27
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,280
The newcomer was none other than

28
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,800
the coroner of Yingtian Prefecture,

29
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,600
Young Master Liu Chuan.

30
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:27,490
Speaking of this Young Master Liu,

31
