32
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:30,320
Ever since Young Master Liu

33
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:32,600
gave Miss Tu the idea of storytelling,

34
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:34,520
the business of Baoyue Tower

35
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,920
