69
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,840
But they never stopped.

70
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:05,520
I think Prince Jia asked me to investigate this

71
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:07,720
not just because of his connection with the Gu family,

72
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,960
but because it involves the Medicine God Society.

73
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:10,720
Prince Jia was

74
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:12,920
the biggest contributor to wiping out the Medicine God Society.

75
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,120
He saved the Emperor,

76
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,400
