78
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:21,520
Now that the Medicine God Society shows signs of a resurgence,

79
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:23,380
he naturally takes it seriously.

80
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,320
Why do I feel like

81
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:28,360
