92
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:51,250
Something happened in the palace.

93
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:04,860
Martial Uncle.

94
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:07,320
This maid was from Consort De's palace.

95
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,960
She died suddenly last night.

96
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:10,920
The people in the palace thought it was a sudden severe illness

97
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,450
and paid no attention to it.

98
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,060
Your Highness.

99
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,980
Your Highness.

100
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:18,240
I saw all of this with my own eyes.

101
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:21,320
This is the Book of Life and Death left by the King of Hell.

102
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,520
I have already reported this to His Majesty.

103
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,640
But His Majesty is busy with the new policies

104
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,920
and has no time to attend to it.

105
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,580
He only said

106
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,920
that such trivial matters

107
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:29,180
are best handled by the Empress Dowager.

108
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:31,760
This emperor is quite sarcastic.

109
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:35,370
Brother Liu.

110
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:39,880
Uncle Master,

111
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,360
this maid's name

112
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,720
is indeed on it.

113
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,460
Your Highness.

114
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:47,040
I observed the Ziwei star last night.

115
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,720
I found it surrounded by black smoke,

116
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:51,159
with a small blood-red crack.

117
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,400
In my opinion,

118
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,680
this isn't a problem that can be solved

119
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,140
with just one or two lives.

120
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:56,080
I'd say,

121
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:57,200
everyone on this Book of Life

122
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,520
and Death will...

123
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,240
Uncle Master.

124
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,760
I've also heard rumors

125
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:12,720
that someone in the palace saw the Palace of Hell at midnight.

126
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,800
Then Brother Liu,

127
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,080
this time,

128
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,680
I'll have to trouble you.

129
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:30,400
Cinnabar.

130
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:32,720
Applied with a brush after death,

131
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,520
dotted on the center of the brow.

132
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,320
There are bruises around the eyes,

133
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,520
and facial swelling.

134
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:42,260
Increased intracranial pressure caused facial congestion.

135
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:44,960
Petechial hemorrhage in the conjunctiva.

136
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,440
Initial assessment

137
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,520
shows the cause of death is the same.

138
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:49,440
Right here.

139
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:52,440
It looks somewhat familiar.

140
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:55,060
The last thing I want to see

141
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:57,200
is the same situation happening again.

142
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:57,720
Come on.

143
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,860
It's exactly the same.

144
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,610
Both were poisoned.

145
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:51,440
So you mean...

146
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:54,520
This has nothing to do with the Book of Life and Death.

147
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:56,920
But it is inextricably linked to Skull Grass.

148
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:58,000
Skull Grass?

149
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:01,980
Could it be because of the Medicine God Society?

150
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,200
His Majesty should have wiped out

151
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:06,040
the Medicine God Society at that time.

152
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:08,240
However, the Medicine God Society's influence was extensive.

153
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,800
Plus, His Majesty was being magnanimous

154
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:11,800
and implementing new policies at the time,

155
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:13,730
so this matter was left unsettled.

156
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:17,650
It seems Prince Jia has many complaints about the new policies.

157
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,920
His Majesty has great ambitions.

158
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:20,920
As his subject,

159
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:22,680
I naturally have to support him.

160
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:23,520
It's just that

161
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:25,880
some things need to be prioritized.

162
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:27,120
Haste makes waste.

163
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,040
You should quickly come with me

164
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:34,300
to the palace to see the Empress Dowager.

165
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,960
Don't make a fuss.

166
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:44,000
Don't lose your dignity as a Noble Consort.

167
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,360
People die in this palace

168
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,520
