169
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,120
But I am scared.

170
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:51,280
That person died right in my hall.

171
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:52,780
What are you afraid of?

172
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:55,760
Since the Emperor wants to implement new policies,

173
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:56,960
