174
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,080
As he is unwell,

175
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:00,560
I am acting on his behalf.

176
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,040
This inner palace

177
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:04,040
must not fall into chaos.

178
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:08,080
Your Grace,

179
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,000
I am in charge of disaster relief.

180
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:13,800
and pacifying important court officials dissatisfied with the New Policies,

181
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:15,800
so there was no time to manage palace affairs.

182
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:17,730
Please deal with this, Your Grace.

183
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,700
The officials in the court

184
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:21,920
are constantly arguing over the New Policies.

185
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:24,050
Fortunately, you are here to mediate.

186
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,580
It has been hard on you.

187
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:28,970
For the state of His Majesty and the Empress Dowager,

188
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:31,320
I would gladly die ten thousand deaths.

189
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,240
According to the Prince of Jia,

190
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,720
are you attributing everything

191
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:37,440
to the New Policies implemented by His Majesty?

192
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,720
I forgot.

193
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:41,480
My lord, it is because you supported His Majesty

194
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,640
and Wang Anshi's New Policies

195
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:45,300
that you slowly climbed your way up the cabinet.

196
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,440
No wonder.

197
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,640
Do you want me,

198
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,880
like Sima Guang and Su Shi and his son,

199
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,360
to be imprisoned just because of a few sincere words

200
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:55,920
that you made an issue out of?

201
00:10:57,520 --> 00:10:58,520
I wouldn't dare.

202
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,600
It's just that the Prince of Jia has always sympathized with

203
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:02,880
the rebels who oppose His Majesty's New Policies.

204
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,200
I'm just worried that

205
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,640
if this matter

206
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,440
is the work of people with ulterior motives

207
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:10,440
spreading rumors to oppose His Majesty's New Policies,

208
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,720
may I ask if the Prince of Jia

209
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:13,040
can be impartial?

210
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:14,360
Enough.

211
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:16,080
The New Policies.

212
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:18,320
I am tired of hearing about them.

213
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,480
These two matters

214
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:21,440
should not be mixed up.

215
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:25,080
How is the investigation going?

216
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:26,720
Your Majesty,

217
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:27,760
I have brought

218
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,640
Liu Chuan, bearer of the Emperor's golden sword,

219
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:30,560
to see you.

220
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:31,800
Send him in.

221
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:37,840
Oh my God.

222
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,120
This sister is actually the Empress Dowager.

223
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:41,050
He is going to cause trouble again.

224
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:42,640
Sister?

225
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,280
Insolent!

226
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,720
I am just too shocked.

227
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:49,800
That's why I lost my composure a bit.

228
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:51,120
Sister Empress Dowager,

229
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,240
you look radiant

230
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,520
and your skin is so firm.

231
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:54,720
When I came in just now,

232
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:56,580
I thought you were some princess.

233
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:57,920
If you,

234
00:11:58,120 --> 00:12:00,400
published your skincare secrets,

235
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,720
women across the whole Great Song,

236
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,720
from 16

237
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:03,760
to 60,

238
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:05,650
would go crazy fighting for it.

239
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,080
Is that so?

240
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:12,200
The Empress Dowager naturally outshines everyone in the harem.

241
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:15,600
I was even afraid calling you 'sister' would make you sound old.

242
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,860
I truly deserve to die.

243
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:19,160
You certainly have a way with words.

244
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:21,960
I was just expressing my true feelings.

245
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:23,080
Liu Chuan,

246
00:12:23,520 --> 00:12:25,400
I have also heard that you

247
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:27,480
solved several major cases in a row.

248
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:30,040
Your talent matches Prince Zhuoran's.

249
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,360
Even Vice Minister Gu

250
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,320
highly praises you.

251
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:35,560
Prince Jia also appreciates you very much,

252
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:38,560
and even the Emperor bestowed a golden sword upon you.

253
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:40,380
You are quite impressive.

254
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:42,320
You flatter me, Empress Dowager.

255
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,720
The Emperor has a good eye for talent.

256
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:44,600
He must have inherited

257
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:46,330
your excellent genes, Sister.

258
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,640
Reporting to the Empress Dowager,

259
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:52,320
Liu Chuan has found some clues

260
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:54,240
suspected to be related to the Yaoshen Society.

261
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:55,320
Medicine God Cult.

262
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:58,840
The Medicine God Cult wasn't completely wiped out back then.

263
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,970
Now there are signs of its resurgence.

264
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:04,100
The cases of Liu Chuan and Qiuyue can prove this.

265
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:09,600
This case in the palace

266
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:11,850
and the previous victims I've seen

267
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,920
were indeed killed by poisons

268
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,440
developed from skull grass.

269
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,400
Skull grass

270
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:19,380
is exactly what the Medicine God Cult worships.

271
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:22,080
Back then,

272
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:24,040
in exterminating the Medicine God Cult

273
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:26,000
and restoring stability to the state,

274
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:28,060
you made the greatest contribution.

275
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,480
Do you have any ideas?

276
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:30,480
Report!

277
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:34,580
Your Grace.

278
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,440
News just came from the Imperial Hospital.

279
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,960
An imperial physician died suddenly.

280
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,090
I have confirmed it.

281
00:13:39,760 --> 00:13:40,560
His name

282
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,840
